## PeopleMine production environment variables
## Copy this file to `.env.production` on the server and fill in real values.

## PostgreSQL (Alibaba Cloud ApsaraDB RDS for PostgreSQL)
## Format:
## postgresql://USERNAME:PASSWORD@HOST:PORT/DATABASE?schema=public
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://db_user:db_password@pgm-xxxxxxxxxxxx.pg.rds.aliyuncs.com:5432/peoplemine?schema=public

## Session encryption secret
## Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
SESSION_SECRET=replace-with-a-long-random-string
## Set to true only when the app is served over HTTPS.
SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE=false

## Alibaba Cloud SMS
## AccessKey pair comes from Alibaba Cloud AccessKey management.
ALIYUN_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
ALIYUN_ACCESS_KEY_SECRET=

## SMS sign and template code come from Alibaba Cloud SMS console.
ALIYUN_SMS_SIGN_NAME=
ALIYUN_SMS_TEMPLATE_CODE=

## Qwen / DashScope
QWEN_API_KEY=
QWEN_BASE_URL=https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/compatible-mode/v1
